{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":817,"text":"When I was only three or four,"},{"time":3285,"text":"I fell in love with poetry,"},{"time":5777,"text":"with the rhythms\nand the music of language;"},{"time":8912,"text":"with the power of metaphor and of imagery,"},{"time":12579,"text":"poetry being the essence\nof communication --"},{"time":15365,"text":"the discipline, the distillation."},{"time":18999,"text":"And all these years later,\nthe poems I'll read today"},{"time":21985,"text":"are from my just-finished\nseventh book of poetry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26199,"text":"Well, five years ago, I was diagnosed\nwith Parkinson's disease."},{"time":30874,"text":"Though there's no cure yet,"},{"time":32818,"text":"advances in treatment\nare really impressive."},{"time":35985,"text":"But you can imagine\nthat I was appalled to learn"},{"time":38999,"text":"that women are largely\nleft out of research trials,"},{"time":43517,"text":"despite gender-specific\nmedical findings having demonstrated"},{"time":47062,"text":"that we are not actually just small men --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":49746,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51866,"text":"who happen to have\ndifferent reproductive systems."},{"time":55142,"text":"Gender-specific medicine\nis good for men, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58325,"text":"But you bring to a crisis\nthe person you already are,"},{"time":63102,"text":"including the, yes, momentum\nthat you've learned to invoke"},{"time":66999,"text":"through passionate caring\nand through action,"},{"time":70332,"text":"both of which require\nbut also create energy."},{"time":75470,"text":"So as an activist, I began working\nwith the Parkinson's Disease Foundation --"},{"time":79780,"text":"that's pdf.org --"},{"time":81985,"text":"to create a major initiative to put women\non the Parkinson's disease map."},{"time":89819,"text":"And as a poet, I began working\nwith this subject matter,"},{"time":93068,"text":"finding it tragic, hilarious,\nsometimes even joyful."},{"time":98136,"text":"I do not feel diminished by Parkinson's;"},{"time":100747,"text":"I feel distilled by it,"},{"time":103396,"text":"and I actually very much\nlike the woman I'm distilling into."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109528,"text":"\"No Signs of Struggle\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":112569,"text":"Growing small requires enormity of will:"},{"time":116643,"text":"just sitting still\nin the doctor's waiting room"},{"time":119255,"text":"watching the future shuffle in and out,"},{"time":122865,"text":"watching it stoop; stare at you"},{"time":125632,"text":"while you try not to look."},{"time":128213,"text":"Rare is an exchange:"},{"time":129880,"text":"a smile of brief, wry recognition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133917,"text":"You are the new kid on the block."},{"time":136192,"text":"Everyone here was you once."},{"time":138791,"text":"You are still learning that growing small\nrequires a largeness of spirit"},{"time":143022,"text":"you can't fit into yet:"},{"time":145505,"text":"acceptance of irritating help\nfrom those who love you;"},{"time":149478,"text":"giving way and over, but not up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153494,"text":"You've swallowed hard the contents\nof the \"Drink Me\" bottle,"},{"time":156746,"text":"and felt yourself shrink."},{"time":159576,"text":"Now, familiar furniture looms,"},{"time":162343,"text":"floors tilt, and doorknobs yield only\nwhen wrestled round with both hands."},{"time":167685,"text":"It demands colossal patience,\nall this growing small:"},{"time":172579,"text":"your diminished sleep at night,"},{"time":174499,"text":"your handwriting, your voice, your height."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178668,"text":"You are more the incredible\nshrinking woman"},{"time":181917,"text":"than the Buddhist mystic,\nserene, making do with less."},{"time":185864,"text":"Less is not always more."},{"time":189560,"text":"Yet in this emptying space,\nspace glimmers,"},{"time":194164,"text":"becoming visible."},{"time":196115,"text":"Here is a place behind the eyes\nof those accustomed"},{"time":199498,"text":"by what some would call diminishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203468,"text":"It is a place of merciless poetry,"},{"time":207167,"text":"a gift of presence previously ignored,"},{"time":210510,"text":"drowned in the daily clutter."},{"time":213357,"text":"Here every gesture needs intention,"},{"time":216462,"text":"is alive with consciousness."},{"time":218886,"text":"Nothing is automatic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221192,"text":"You can spot it\nin the provocation of a button,"},{"time":224685,"text":"an arm poking at a sleeve,"},{"time":226922,"text":"a balancing act at a night-time curb\nwhile negotiating the dark."},{"time":232133,"text":"Feats of such modest valor,"},{"time":235191,"text":"who would suspect them to be exercises\nin an intimate, fierce discipline,"},{"time":240519,"text":"a metaphysics of being relentlessly aware?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":244667,"text":"Such understated power here,"},{"time":247476,"text":"in these tottering dancers\nwho exert stupendous effort"},{"time":251788,"text":"on tasks most view as insignificant."},{"time":255572,"text":"Such quiet beauty here, in these,"},{"time":258937,"text":"my soft-voiced, stiff-limbed people;"},{"time":263234,"text":"such resolve masked by each placid face."},{"time":267937,"text":"There is immensity required\nin growing small,"},{"time":272554,"text":"so bent on such unbending grace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276020,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":282343,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283945,"text":"This one is called\n\"On Donating My Brain to Science.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":287152,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":289058,"text":"Not a problem."},{"time":291349,"text":"Skip over all the pages\nreassuring religious people."},{"time":295280,"text":"Already a universal donor:\nkidneys, corneas, liver, lungs,"},{"time":299060,"text":"tissue, heart, veins, whatever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302097,"text":"Odd that the modest brain never\nimagined its unique value in research,"},{"time":307599,"text":"maybe saving someone else from what it is\nthey're not quite sure I have."},{"time":311937,"text":"Flattering, that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313673,"text":"So fill in the forms,"},{"time":315842,"text":"drill through the answers,"},{"time":317725,"text":"trill out a blithe spirit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320021,"text":"And slice me, dice me,\nspread me on your slides."},{"time":324703,"text":"Find what I'm trying to tell you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326994,"text":"Earn me, learn me, scan me,\nsquint through your lens."},{"time":332015,"text":"Uncover what I'd hint at if I could."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334718,"text":"Be my guest, do your best,\nharvest me, track the clues."},{"time":339206,"text":"This was a good brain while alive."},{"time":341704,"text":"This was a brain that paid its dues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344084,"text":"So slice me, dice me,\nsmear me on your slides,"},{"time":348999,"text":"stain me, explain me, drain me like a cup."},{"time":352544,"text":"Share me, hear me:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354644,"text":"I want to be used\nI want to be used"},{"time":357268,"text":"I want to be used\nup."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360395,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":367435,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":369669,"text":"And this one's called \"The Ghost Light.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":374229,"text":"Lit from within is the sole secure way"},{"time":377803,"text":"to traverse dark matter."},{"time":380424,"text":"Some life forms -- certain mushrooms,\nsnails, jellyfish, worms --"},{"time":385445,"text":"glow bioluminescent,"},{"time":387741,"text":"and people as well;"},{"time":389534,"text":"we emit infra-red light\nfrom our most lucent selves."},{"time":394676,"text":"Our tragedy is we can't see it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398406,"text":"We see by reflecting."},{"time":400972,"text":"We need biofluorescence\nto show our true colors."},{"time":405400,"text":"External illumination can distort, though."},{"time":408527,"text":"When gravity bends light,"},{"time":410553,"text":"huge galaxy clusters\ncan act as telescopes,"},{"time":414186,"text":"elongating background images\nof star systems to faint arcs --"},{"time":419387,"text":"a lensing effect"},{"time":420565,"text":"like viewing distant street lamps\nthrough a glass of wine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425535,"text":"A glass of wine or two now makes me weave"},{"time":428266,"text":"as if acting the drunkard's part;"},{"time":431152,"text":"as if, besotted with unrequited love"},{"time":434522,"text":"for the dynamic Turner canvasses\nspied out by the Hubble,"},{"time":438631,"text":"I could lurch down a city street set"},{"time":440936,"text":"without provoking\nevery pedestrian walk-on stare."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445924,"text":"Stare as long as you need to."},{"time":448442,"text":"If you think about it, walking,\neven standing, is illogical --"},{"time":453865,"text":"such tiny things, feet! --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455865,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":457806,"text":"especially when one's body\nis not al dente anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461741,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":465729,"text":"Besides, creature of extremes and excess,"},{"time":468875,"text":"I've always thought Apollo\nbeautiful but boring,"},{"time":471935,"text":"and a bit of a dumb blonde."},{"time":474771,"text":"Dionysians don't do balance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478923,"text":"Balance, in other words,\nhas never been my strong point."},{"time":483104,"text":"But I digress."},{"time":484296,"text":"More and more these days,"},{"time":485535,"text":"digression seems\nthe most direct route through"},{"time":488557,"text":"from where I've lost or found myself"},{"time":490658,"text":"out of place, mind, turn, time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495222,"text":"Place your foot just so,\nmind how you turn:"},{"time":499582,"text":"too swift a swivel can bring you down."},{"time":503206,"text":"Take your time ushering the audience out,"},{"time":506158,"text":"saying goodbye to the actors."},{"time":509048,"text":"The ghost light"},{"time":510223,"text":"is what they call the single bulb"},{"time":512033,"text":"hanging above the bare stage\nin an empty theater."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516655,"text":"In the empty theater of such a night,"},{"time":518992,"text":"waking to meet no external radiance,"},{"time":522834,"text":"this is the final struggle left to win,"},{"time":526050,"text":"this the sole beacon\nto beckon the darkness in"},{"time":529309,"text":"and let the rest begin,"},{"time":531978,"text":"this the lens through which at last\nto see both Self and Other"},{"time":536955,"text":"arrayed with the bright stain\nof original sin:"},{"time":541599,"text":"lit from within."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544870,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":552725,"text":"And this is the last one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554639,"text":"\"This Dark Hour\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":557513,"text":"Late summer, 4 A.M."},{"time":560674,"text":"The rain slows to a stop,"},{"time":563044,"text":"dripping still from the broad leaves"},{"time":565316,"text":"of blue hostas unseen\nin the garden's dark."},{"time":569259,"text":"Barefoot, careful\non the slick slate slabs,"},{"time":572977,"text":"I need no light, I know the way,"},{"time":576284,"text":"stoop by the mint bed,"},{"time":578187,"text":"scoop a fistful of moist earth,"},{"time":581016,"text":"then grope for a chair,"},{"time":582748,"text":"spread a shawl, and sit,"},{"time":585426,"text":"breathing in the wet green August air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590240,"text":"This is the small, still hour"},{"time":593254,"text":"before the newspaper\nlands in the vestibule like a grenade,"},{"time":597092,"text":"the phone shrills, the computer screen\nblinks and glares awake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602643,"text":"There is this hour:"},{"time":604847,"text":"poem in my head, soil in my hand:"},{"time":608847,"text":"unnamable fullness."},{"time":611662,"text":"This hour, when blood of my blood"},{"time":614269,"text":"bone of bone, child grown\nto manhood now --"},{"time":618325,"text":"stranger, intimate,\nnot distant but apart --"},{"time":623813,"text":"lies safe, off dreaming melodies"},{"time":627571,"text":"while love sleeps, safe, in his arms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":631735,"text":"To have come to this place,"},{"time":634364,"text":"lived to this moment:"},{"time":636479,"text":"immeasurable lightness."},{"time":639392,"text":"The density of black starts to blur umber."},{"time":642789,"text":"Tentative, a cardinal's coloratura,"},{"time":645791,"text":"then the mourning dove's elegy."},{"time":648390,"text":"Sable glimmers toward grey;"},{"time":650804,"text":"objects emerge, trailing shadows;"},{"time":653996,"text":"night ages toward day."},{"time":656540,"text":"The city stirs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658958,"text":"There will be other dawns,\nnights, gaudy noons."},{"time":663460,"text":"Likely, I'll lose my way."},{"time":665860,"text":"There will be stumbling, falling,"},{"time":668296,"text":"cursing the dark."},{"time":670490,"text":"Whatever comes,"},{"time":672134,"text":"there was this hour when nothing mattered,"},{"time":676105,"text":"all was unbearably dear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":679890,"text":"And when I'm done with daylights,"},{"time":682140,"text":"should those who loved me\ngrieve too long a while,"},{"time":687125,"text":"let them remember that I had this hour --"},{"time":690378,"text":"this dark, perfect hour --"},{"time":694010,"text":"and smile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696418,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697596,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}